Awesome! As much as possible, let's stick the the OGL rulebooks. Since this is a marketing exercise that doesn't need to be official, these will just be shared using a link and not show in the marketplace either.

Here's an unlisted chatbot I created using the D&D rules. @Nathaniel do you think you'll be able to test it and see whether the response quality is good? @Bas we can then do a small test where we share this in a few subreddits and see the response.

D&D Rulebook - Chatbot - AI Hub (instabase.com) (https://aihub.instabase.com/hub/apps/74dd9df3-026c-4990-a76e-a3630f2726b9)
